# DESIGN_REVIEW_RECORD.md

## Purpose

Record design-stage review results for {{ project.name }}.

This optional template reviews design documents only. It does not create new design outputs, implementation artifacts, runtime tests, gates, examples, or live target behavior.

## Scope

- Reviewed documents.
- Design-only compliance result.
- Source-use compliance result.
- Sensitive information check result.
- Prohibited artifact check result.
- Document-by-document PASS/PARTIAL/BLOCKED findings.
- Recommended next design-stage outputs.

