## Prohibited Content

- Runtime implementation.
- Application code.
- C# source, solution, project, XAML, build assets, scripts, binaries, or executable packaging.
- PLC/device code.
- Live target write support or external mutation.
- GitHub Actions or cloud CI.
- Eval harness implementation.
- Raw source bulk copy.
- IP, port, tag value, live parameter, secret, private input, live config, credential, account, equipment detail, or sensitive requirement text.

## Approval Boundary

This review can recommend whether more design-stage documentation is ready. It cannot approve implementation, profile creation, example creation, render integration, gate implementation, CI, or live target access.

